1.10	Bishop_of_Llandaff_Church_in_Wales_High_School	Bishop of Llandaff Church in Wales High School	Bishop of Llandaff Church in Wales High School (Welsh: ) is a Church in Wales, Christian faith comprehensive school in the Llandaff area of Cardiff, Wales It takes both male and female students aged 11 to 18, from Cardiff and surrounding areas such as Vale of Glamorgan, Pontypridd and Bridgend. While the school is supported and partially controlled by the Church in Wales, it includes students from other Christian denominations.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/44/Cardiff_University_main_building.jpg/100px-Cardiff_University_main_building.jpg
